      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "ELITE ARNOTT (4) doesn't have the best strike-rate but recent form is sound. Has hit the frame at his last four runs, the latest finishing third (22.33) at this track. Form here at the trip sound including two wins. Remains without a win from the draw but has been in the placings four times from four attempts. Nicely placed to grab a well-deserved win. STUBBORN MOUSE (2) was prominent throughout when an impressive winner two back but could manage only midfield last time when finished 4th and beaten 5 lengths at this track (22.52). Comes out of a solid form race last start. Cannot be taken lightly. ROXY KEEPING (1) was drawn the middle last start but pinged the lids and recorded an all-the-way win (22.12) at this track in a Novice race over 381m. Recorded one of the quickest times on the card in scoring last start. Capable of going well again. BOUJEE DELUSIONS (5) can fill a top-three spot.",
